{"tid":1407664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［港島人］千祈唔好塞呢幾度 我要搭巴士番工","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:49:02.000Z","uid":142073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b21589294f8d81771dc0e8e2dac0685ba3bcce5","tid":1407664,"uid":142073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"1. 由柴灣講起<br />\n柴灣、小西灣、<span style=\"font-size: large;\">杏花邨</span>都勁多藍絲廢佬&amp;中產<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地最鍾意番工</span><br />\n主要巴士路綫會經<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新翠花園對開嘅迴旋處</span></span>上東區走廊/柴灣道<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B61i7iK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB61i7iK.png&h=85651fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好喺條橋扇手跌枝油或者玻璃樽落去</span></span> <br />\n如果有意外發生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要用圍欄圍住危險的地方</span>唔好令啲車炒埋一碟<br />\n而家柴灣區到處都係地盤 唔好偷人地啲圍欄啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">永泰路</span></span><br />\n788 789 118p 85 82x 都會經呢度<span style=\"font-size: large;\">特快送啲人走</span><br />\n而家果度又係有地盤做緊野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好搞地盤啲工程牌</span></span>又大塊又重 容乜易有意外<br />\n2. 第二個要講就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">北角英皇道</span></span> <br />\n就算柴灣冇人塞到 都有唔少巴士線會經呢度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQsN0Fs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQsN0Fs.png&h=d82388b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東區走廊落北角嘅車 平日peak hour都塞塞地 大家要小心唔好整塞呢度<br />\n點解北角都要搞？因為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">北角有警署 但英皇道多藍絲民居 有催淚彈比佢地嘆下 話唔定藍轉黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n3. 下一站<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天后</span></span><br />\n有維園比大家晨運 唔係唔去牙<br />\n但地鐵站對條英皇道<span style=\"color: red;\">好多巴士搞到成日塞</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLyERPB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLyERPB.png&h=40df59cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且一塞就塞到上東區走廊<span style=\"color: red;\">而且有地鐵站口，你話真係塞呢度會幾煩呢</span><br />\n4. 入南區嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅拿道巴士站</span></span><br />\n呢度成日都有人過馬路阻住啲巴士行<br />\n要入南區都幾難搞<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hrV9B9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hrV9B9.png&h=df29cc28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5. 灣仔<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">告士打道</span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">係我地要重點保護嘅</span></span><br />\n你都知果兩幢政府大樓有幾重要<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEjTWiy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEjTWiy.png&h=13c9a019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家記住be water 不死守 見到狗狗即刻走</span></span>"},{"pid":"593094f1edd57fe92616d4686fd142c06cddf08d","tid":1407664,"uid":150083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:49:02.000Z","msg":"推"}]}